Text: Where Do I Send the Checkthanks for the phone message last week We are excited to have you back in Houston Cant wait to pop in on you Sunday evenings with a bottle of bubbly or fine wine Got your Christmas email Could you tell us the address to send the check Thanks Hope you had a wonderful Thanksgiving Mike
